{"tid":162553,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"吸血傳銷專呃阿婆,下任特首可唔可以幫我手","createTime":"2017-03-19T11:13:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-20T01:57:34.000Z","uid":92145,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e87bbcb04e718ebd85bdb64ec06f988cd3574719","tid":162553,"uid":92145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T11:13:19.000Z","msg":"各位巴打有冇聽過一間叫JapanLife既傳銷公司?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地間公司雖然唔係好大,但吸金能力就勁到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我老母七十幾歲,早排拎晒成副棺材本比佢地做左個叫短期貨主既存款<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/Vjck5b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FVjck5b.jpg&h=3444cabd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n6厘息,個個月派息,可以隨時拎返現錢走,入面全部都係D廢老口講愛國但就送錢去日本公司<br />\n我拎刀自殺叫我老母拎返D錢出黎,佢地就話我老母跟左弱智仔去大陸玩,一定要放一年先可以拎走,又話賠呢樣賠果樣,賠埋個老母比你好冇?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n開頭諗住等一年硬食算,諗諗下覺得公司好有問題<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/KgFpWB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FKgFpWB.jpg&h=faa69f09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢地話我老母係短期買左D磁石租出去比人,利息即係租金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拎返個本出黎一定係錢<br />\n但係租左比邊9個都唔撚知,係咁講放心啦有人租架啦<br />\n又話大把人一千幾百萬放入黎,個個月收息好開心"},{"pid":"6f4798a66f11c9df259b0e48f7f802842142cb7a","tid":162553,"uid":51585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T11:15:21.000Z","msg":"G_G<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8abfa50066b111328614f74790cab7f2204e8502","tid":162553,"uid":92145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T11:23:59.000Z","msg":"我盡一切力量去搵有關JapanLife既資料,點知發現佢地日本比政府有類似停業既命令<br />\n<br />\n2016年12月16日 日本新聞<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.news24.jp/articles/2016/12/16/07349296.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.news24.jp%2Farticles%2F2016%2F12%2F16%2F07349296.html&d=cj%2BBBxPbgcFbNOKLHyO8KCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=50f88300\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.news24.jp/articles/2016/12/16/07349296.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://mainichi.jp/articles/20161217/k00/00m/040/042000c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmainichi.jp%2Farticles%2F20161217%2Fk00%2F00m%2F040%2F042000c&d=cj%2BBBxPbgcFbNOKLHyO8KCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=a326c023\" target=\"_blank\">http://mainichi.jp/articles/20161217/k00/00m/040/042000c</a><br />\n<br />\n日本消費者廳2016年12月16日處分報告<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.caa.go.jp/policies/policy/consumer_transaction/release/pdf/161216kouhyou_1.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.caa.go.jp%2Fpolicies%2Fpolicy%2Fconsumer_transaction%2Frelease%2Fpdf%2F161216kouhyou_1.pdf&d=cj%2BBBxPbgcFbNOKLHyO8KCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=a481f606\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.caa.go.jp/policies/policy/consumer_transaction/release/pdf/161216kouhyou_1.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n香港JapanLife發出通告否認,明顯欺騙公眾<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/15672967_116730795492483_949478537150538607_n.jpg?oh=ee09255e9f5b4d275d5f1b9631f76769&amp;oe=58D6AAB5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F15672967_116730795492483_949478537150538607_n.jpg%3Foh%3Dee09255e9f5b4d275d5f1b9631f76769%26oe%3D58D6AAB5&h=dc3018d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nJapanLife繼續係各地吸金,尤其係香港<br />\nJapanLife無視對消費者廳的命令,結果延長對佢地既處罰到2017年12月<br />\n<br />\n2017年3月16日 日本新聞<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fnn-news.com/news/headlines/articles/CONN00352663.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fnn-news.com%2Fnews%2Fheadlines%2Farticles%2FCONN00352663.html&d=cj%2BBBxPbgcFbNOKLHyO8KCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=4af35fde\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.fnn-news.com/news/headlines/articles/CONN00352663.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.news24.jp/articles/2017/03/17/07356724.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.news24.jp%2Farticles%2F2017%2F03%2F17%2F07356724.html&d=cj%2BBBxPbgcFbNOKLHyO8KCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=10c13b7e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.news24.jp/articles/2017/03/17/07356724.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.jiji.com/jc/article?k=2017031601460&amp;g=soc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jiji.com%2Fjc%2Farticle%3Fk%3D2017031601460%26g%3Dsoc&d=cj%2BBBxPbgcFbNOKLHyO8KCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=c1fb44d8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.jiji.com/jc/article?k=2017031601460&amp;g=soc</a><br />\n<br />\n日本消費者廳2017年3月16日處分報告<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.caa.go.jp/policies/policy/consumer_transaction/release/pdf/170317kouhyou_2.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.caa.go.jp%2Fpolicies%2Fpolicy%2Fconsumer_transaction%2Frelease%2Fpdf%2F170317kouhyou_2.pdf&d=cj%2BBBxPbgcFbNOKLHyO8KCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=d7c514d9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.caa.go.jp/policies/policy/consumer_transaction/release/pdf/170317kouhyou_2.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n香港JapanLife再次發出通告欺瞞公眾,繼續在香港吸金<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/8sZN7x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2F8sZN7x.jpg&h=683e7356&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/lY5wPz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FlY5wPz.jpg&h=7ee63d34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n通告上只係強調佢地唔可以做訪問銷售,即係上門推銷<br />\n對處分內容隻字不提,而且不斷話正常營業"},{"pid":"7db3da70606d49d49b6426ebd4d3ab43f79735af","tid":162553,"uid":92145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T11:45:49.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"360c8b3ee0b959a985940ee3bb3f5a6d558de5b4","tid":162553,"uid":92145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T11:59:59.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71a5bcbcff23998c41175572e9a161dcaa0b3531","tid":162553,"uid":92145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T12:21:05.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8bc7013554b0b1fe8761ccf72d0ef8d6900bfd8","tid":162553,"uid":23421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T12:26:23.000Z","msg":"你老母七十幾歲就唔好撚俾佢出街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50d075a2b7e03cc1b59787567751de2dd34b9ad4","tid":162553,"uid":37586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T12:28:59.000Z","msg":"吸金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢次真係吸你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07053d5122b7230bdc7f3ef4b401290de686a090","tid":162553,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T12:29:25.000Z","msg":"擺住一年睇下點先<br />\n到時真係有料到咪算<br />\n無就搞大佢 <br />\n而家咁樣好難講"},{"pid":"610834643cb02289c5952e5475b528d8ba58d12d","tid":162553,"uid":23421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T12:43:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>擺住一年睇下點先<br />\n到時真係有料到咪算<br />\n無就搞大佢 <br />\n而家咁樣好難講</blockquote><br />\n擺一年間公司執鳩左<br />\n啲廢老棺材本都無鳩埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca58759dfbc95dad38edd87a20cd148dd711cdfd","tid":162553,"uid":92732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T12:43:43.000Z","msg":"當買個教訓啦，安慰下你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71d0534f7178c682ccfa39991679b639dee82450","tid":162553,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T12:51:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b781a3ce9f505d4d1af3b7a5ed5a2ceca32839ba","tid":162553,"uid":92145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T12:57:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>擺住一年睇下點先<br />\n到時真係有料到咪算<br />\n無就搞大佢 <br />\n而家咁樣好難講</blockquote><br />\n就係睇到佢比人停業<br />\n香港仲繼續吸廢老錢，成年唔使訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2ad3567c9e7d241ff3bd9663a402633ddc1d766","tid":162553,"uid":92145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T12:58:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢真係派過息比你？<br />\n<br />\n一百幾十萬咪算囉</blockquote><br />\n果到咁多廢老就唔止一百幾十萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9799cb2b09211190a79b7db07fae14b8157e5b70","tid":162553,"uid":88029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T13:03:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fe5ef034fb790eae4cd8ea8ba09c52546df8dec8","tid":162553,"uid":37919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T13:08:21.000Z","msg":"召喚中正巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b7ba4927a1f90bcd13606e527f3bcd3b031afe7","tid":162553,"uid":92145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T13:20:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>龐氏騙局（英語：Ponzi scheme）是非法性質的層壓式推銷或稱「金字塔式騙局」商業推銷模式的一個著名的、成熟的代表案例，發生於20世紀初的美國，但到今日各種變體依舊存在金融市場中。<br />\n<br />\n其運作模式為參與者要先付一筆錢作為入會代價，這與一般的理財會社的會員並無區別，但在龐氏騙局中，所賺的錢是來自其他新加入的參加者，而非公司本身透過業務所賺的錢，即所謂「拆東牆補西牆」。投資者通過不斷吸引新的投資者加入付錢，以支付上線投資者的投資與利潤，初期通常在短時間內獲得回報以利於推行，再逐漸拉長還款時間。隨着更多人加入，資金流入不足支出，當現金總量龐大時尚不足以崩潰，甚至也可以正常投資事業來持續運作，但直到騙局泡沫爆破時，最下線的大量投資者便會蒙受金錢損失。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0152dfa99ba12b7c8fdcd153a7c9d7eff67159e4","tid":162553,"uid":92145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T14:25:59.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"275b721ea14bf0fa0c49bac919c0309d0f00bfd7","tid":162553,"uid":92754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T14:36:02.000Z","msg":"老闆，網上面一早有關於JapanLife搵9人苯柒嘅資料架啦，得閒關心下屋企D老廢，出左事樓主你都有責任 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n搵苯柒報導<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.66163.com/fujian_w/news/fzrb/000107t/5_2.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.66163.com%2Ffujian_w%2Fnews%2Ffzrb%2F000107t%2F5_2.html&d=cj%2BBBxPbgcFbNOKLHyO8KCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=f4a564f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.66163.com/fujian_w/news/fzrb/000107t/5_2.html</a>"},{"pid":"4370b672e9febdf86df159736acef1c633d6b279","tid":162553,"uid":23421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T14:45:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"384531901002705fa0904b090fbd716b8b390f67","tid":162553,"uid":92754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T15:08:56.000Z","msg":"巴打有咩事告佢老味，同間公司玩大佢啦"},{"pid":"5e2988f2a1fca8491eb272ec50c8bd750b7f01f1","tid":162553,"uid":92145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T15:52:57.000Z","msg":"有冇識法律既巴打可以幫下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地咁樣收人錢穩唔穩陣架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feb1274745df3a10fe0fa9ea0e16ef9425b8cd3f","tid":162553,"uid":92145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T01:49:19.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51a12151d2e507378a29d0b281386c116c4e9633","tid":162553,"uid":92754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T01:57:34.000Z","msg":"間垃圾公司有冇存款牌呀，冇既話就犯法架啦，非法集資，你有冇合約post上黎睇下呀？"}]}